colors=c("URI"="blue","Sinusitis"="red")
plt <- ggplot(diffs, aes(x=results.Sinusitis.Estimate, y=-log(results.Sinusitis.Pr...z..))) + 
  geom_point(aes(color="Sinusitis")) + 
  geom_point(aes(x=results.URI.Estimate, y=-log(results.URI.Pr...z..), color="URI")) + 
  ggrepel::geom_text_repel(data=diffs[diffs$results.URI.Pr...z.._p.fdr < 0.05,], aes(x=results.URI.Estimate, y=-log(results.URI.Pr...z..), label=paste(OTU,genus)), size=3, color="blue", box.padding=1) + 
  ggrepel::geom_text_repel(data=diffs[diffs$results.Sinusitis.Pr...z.._p.fdr < 0.05,], aes(x=results.Sinusitis.Estimate, y=-log(results.Sinusitis.Pr...z..), label=paste(OTU, genus)), size=3, color="red", box.padding=1) + 
  xlab("Estimate") +
  ylab("-log(P-value)") + 
  scale_color_manual("Legend",values=colors)
plt
